entry.title: #SONA2020: Part 6 of President Rodrigo Duterte's State of the Nation Address on July 27, 2020

media:group.media:title: #SONA2020: Part 6 of President Rodrigo Duterte's State of the Nation Address on July 27, 2020
media:group.media:description: President Rodrigo Duterte delivered his fifth State of the Nation Address on July 27, 2020. This is the sixth part of his annual speech before a joint session of Congress. Only a limited number of lawmakers attended the SONA in Batasang Pambansa to observe physical distancing and prevent the spread of COVID-19. Congress mounted a hybrid session where others joined through video conferencing.
